# Sprint 59: UI/UX Problems & Solutions
# S59.ptl

v:4
role: planner
gate: OPEN

objective: |
  Modal system: bottom-anchored, dynamic height, scroll under footer with margins;
  Date/Time modal (remove time cancel); Report/Vehicle modals same rules; Objects
  filter list match tracking/reports. Map: full height with transparency under
  header/footer; popup margins; layer switcher flatter. Objects search styling;
  time filter proper format. History Events: restore tabs, back button; Object
  Select history similar to tracking. Object Details: events scroll in own
  container; map/date/info fixed; API check. Loader: circular pulsating,
  increase size on disappear. Tracking: event icons padding, green pulsating
  validation; Player analytics. Theme: single button cycle System→Light→Dark.
  Settings accordion styling. PWA study: screen fill, rotation spacing.
  Refactoring and optimizing code (structure, duplication, performance). Testing.

requires: [FRONTEND_DEV]
invariants: sprints/54/INVARIANTS.md
design-ref: sprints/56/artifacts/S56-Consolidated-Roadmap.md

###############################################################################
# CONTEXT
###############################################################################
epic: E-05-PWA-UI-IMPLEMENTATION
priority: P0
source: UI/UX Problems & Solutions Sprint Prompt
target: navitrack-apps (paths.code per project.config.yml)

